unacceptable levels of hazardous materials kolesar said 
dosimeters which are used in many cases to detect toxic materials 
only reveal exposure after the fact 
another possible application is in developing lighter and 
stronger metals by combining existing metals he said there is an 
optimum cure temperature and cure length cycle which the chip 
could be used to pinpoint 
it also could be used to ferret out bombs by the chemicals they 
emit current detectors for measuring contaminants are mostly bulky 
and vulnerable to being confused by the presence of more than one 
chemical he said 
